00:24:19.552 --> 00:24:23.432
mark the EBI macrophage in green, and we can flow

415
00:24:23.512 --> 00:24:27.472
cytometry sorting out. We co-culture with the tumor, and we show that indeed

416
00:24:27.482 --> 00:24:31.444
they promote tumor growth in vitro.We can then also use GERA mice

417
00:24:31.453 --> 00:24:35.044
to deplete those EBI macrophages because GERA mice

