00:24:38.504 --> 00:24:41.884
And then if you use GERA mice to deplete EBI macrophage compared to

420
00:24:42.024 --> 00:24:45.483
normal mice without the GERA T cell to deplete the

421
00:24:45.984 --> 00:24:46.344
IMAC,

